Global Smart Pet Dryer Market Insights
Smart Pet Dryer Market size was valued at USD 0.75 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Smart Pet Dryer Market Overview
The global smart pet dryer market is experiencing rapid growth, with a projected market value of USD 850 million by 2030, expanding at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 8.3% from 2023 to 2030. The increasing awareness of pet grooming, the rise in pet ownership, and the growing trend of advanced pet care technologies are driving this market. Additionally, consumer preference for convenience and innovative pet care solutions are propelling the demand for smart pet dryers. These devices offer advanced features such as adjustable temperature control, rapid drying times, and user-friendly interfaces, making them highly popular among pet owners.

